      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in flawless condition\u2014I've babied it since day one, so it looks and drives just like it did the day I brought it home! It's spotless inside and out, and I promise you won't find another one this well-cared for. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you've gotta come see this one for yourself!",
