      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional FD3S chassis featuring the legendary sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. This specimen exhibits flawless mechanical synchronization; the secondary turbocharger transition is seamless, with no boost leaks or actuator hesitation. The drivetrain remains stock and robust, featuring a crisp five-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh and a verified compression test yielding high, consistent PSI across all rotor faces. The aluminum double-wishbone suspension retains its factory-fresh kinematics, providing the precise feedback these icons are known for. With a pristine undercarriage and zero modifications, this is a collector-grade example of 90s JDM performance engineering.",
